snippet.title: Pervez Musharraf: India Should Not Underestimate Pakistan after Pathankot Attack

localized.description:
India should not underestimate Pakistan after Pathankot attack, says Former Pakistan President General (retired) Pervez Musharraf. Speaking in an interview to a Pakistani news channel, Musharraf said Pakistan is also a victim of terrorism.
